very good. contains a some bachata, pop, reggaeton, salsa, merengue. lots of good tracks. only 1 or two stuffed up (eg advert at the start of track 12). well worth a download.

esta bien. contiene una variedad grande de estilos como son: bachata, pop, reggaeton, salsa, merengue. hay muchas buenas canciones. solo un o dos tienen mala calidad, p.ej. el #12 tiene un anuncio para empezar. en mi opinion vale la pena bajarlo.

thanks for sharing with us, remember to seed to 1:1 even though you are behind a firewall.
